"{\"uid\": \"huffingtonpost.co.uk-entry-tom-daley-returns-confirms-retirement-olympic-diving-paris_uk_66ba11abe4b0eabd23939848\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Entertainment Editor An emotionalTom Daleyhas confirmed that he is retiring from the world of professional diving.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Entertainment Editor An emotionalTom Daleyhas\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"professional diving\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom has been diving competitively since he was a teenager, and in the2024 Olympicspicked up a silver medal, making him one of the few athletes with a bronze, silver and gold to his name.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"the few athletes\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"his name\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After returning home from Paris on Monday morning, he was interviewed at London's St Pancras station by BBC News, where he opened up about his decision to retire from the sport for which he has been synonymous for more than 15 years.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 331, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999982202914374, \"rank\": 1.7797118120545152e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999746713396661, \"rank\": 2.227241192936099e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.999201089596182, \"rank\": 0.0007956766458971348, \"text\": \"BBC News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Monday morning\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 15 years\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fighting back tears, he admitted: \\\"It's hard to talk about.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am [proud of myself].\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, it's really hard to talk about, but you know, I have to hang it up some time.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am very proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked for his immediate plans upon returning to the UK, he shared: \\\"I want to be with my family.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8956497320024155, \"rank\": 0.11426275729763442, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his immediate plans\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really excited to be able to spend some time with them, and be able to feel a bit normal for a couple of days.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But yeah, it's just very overwhelming.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not mean for it all to time out exactly like this, but yeah, I just feel very proud of my career.\\\"\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Right now, obviously, it's just a lot,\\\" he shared.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a lot\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I am really happy with how everything's gone, I just think it's always hard when you say goodbye to your sport.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"goodbye\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"your sport\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, yeah\\u2026 lots of things to process.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"So, yeah\\u2026 lots\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it's the right time, this year felt like such a bonus.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"such a bonus\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I got to compete in front of my family, my kids, and I got to be flag-bearer.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"flag-bearer\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So bucket list ticked off on every occasion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bucket list\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"every occasion\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very happy, but it's hard to talk when you have loved something so much,\\\" Tom added.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an emotional watch!Tom Daley spoke to the BBC moments after announcing he will retire from diving.#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/hZfHABBpN0 This year marked Tom's fifth time at the Olympics, having first competed in Beijing back in 2008, and winning his first medal four years later.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6711342285491424e-33, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 1627, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9698763004881001, \"rank\": 0.016322167639023596, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998602275254325, \"rank\": 0.0001397920073538163, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q16